	<div class="commentBody">
		<div id="comment_body_64771440">The big problem with Science today is the proliferation of papers. It doesn't matter if it is accurate and correct: if it isn't original or novel then it still contributes to the information pollution just as much as if it was inaccurate or downright fantasy.
<p>
